{"tid":802210,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★返工=?? 外判工未做滿3個月 被要求賠千元「培訓費」","createTime":"2018-09-01T09:46:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-01T11:55:11.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"88afe6eba9b4f7ea763a0bd333a0b4ce4522f9d3","tid":802210,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T09:46:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180901/large/1535780981_fb24.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180901%2Flarge%2F1535780981_fb24.png&h=bef72d75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有高鐵西九站外判車站助理向《蘋果》揭發，負責高鐵西九站保安及車站營運的外判商國際永勝護衛管理公司，疑要求外判員工簽下「不平等合約」，僱傭合約設計成不設試用期，任何人上班就算1天離職，必須提供1個月通知期；<span style=\"color: red;\">而未做滿3個月離職，更要向資方賠償1,000元培訓費</span>用。有關員工直斥，培訓是由港鐵提供，不滿外判商反向員工索償，批評做法無理。<br />\n<br />\n國際永勝護衛發言人稱，相關安排是為控制流失率，做法亦符合法例要求，強調公司有酌情機制豁免員工相關費用，幾乎所有離職的高鐵外判員工都獲豁免。港鐵發言人稱，港鐵與外判商會按服務合約處理培訓成本，任何情況下均不會外判員工收取任何費用。<br />\n<br />\n陳先生(化名)曾任職港鐵外判車站助理6年，他近期獲高鐵西九站外判服務商「國際永勝」聘用為高鐵站車站助理，並獲安排接受訓練。他指，留意到西九站外判商的聘用合約條款比其他港鐵外判商苛刻，包括僱用安排設計成沒有試用期，任何員工離職必須提供1個月通知期，否則要繳付代通知金。同時合約內更列明，若員工未做滿3個月就離職，公司將「收回支付課程之行政費1,000元」。他斥，外判員工一般都要接受港鐵訓練及考核才能正式在車站工作，但他過去在其他外判商工作時，未試過有公司向離職員工收培訓費，質疑高鐵外判公司刻薄。據他了解，有同事上班一天因事離職，亦被追討培訓費，最終以當天工資抵償。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180901/58632633\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180901%2F58632633&d=q6KOYGt1kL0Myl74aCbbNhv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=f0d341e1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180901%2F58632633&h=91849df2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180901/58632633</a>"},{"pid":"c401cc533513cc9ef0fa3750fc2efd660c4ae9ff","tid":802210,"uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T09:48:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/12/164607_750ddbf3ac6d9374f8e9193aa94ad2a7.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F12%2F164607_750ddbf3ac6d9374f8e9193aa94ad2a7.gif&h=e4784eb0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"42edeed410e1f6e5dda6358bf3903fcc65302737","tid":802210,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T09:52:05.000Z","msg":"揾工用 太空卡，用床位地址最安全"},{"pid":"797154b3243530df38de5148428f86036b8cf900","tid":802210,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42edeed410e1f6e5dda6358bf3903fcc65302737","tid":802210,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T09:52:05.000Z","msg":"揾工用 太空卡，用床位地址最安全"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T09:58:23.000Z","msg":"你搵緊咩工"},{"pid":"2707b0c3732f9b7ec2354ade0fd0a89b0a3b945b","tid":802210,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"797154b3243530df38de5148428f86036b8cf900","tid":802210,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42edeed410e1f6e5dda6358bf3903fcc65302737","tid":802210,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T09:52:05.000Z","msg":"揾工用 太空卡，用床位地址最安全"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T09:58:23.000Z","msg":"你搵緊咩工"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T09:59:03.000Z","msg":"以前"},{"pid":"ed4550ff6c1d69ecac853a6b558dde7f2ba27cae","tid":802210,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2707b0c3732f9b7ec2354ade0fd0a89b0a3b945b","tid":802210,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"797154b3243530df38de5148428f86036b8cf900","tid":802210,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42edeed410e1f6e5dda6358bf3903fcc65302737","tid":802210,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T09:52:05.000Z","msg":"揾工用 太空卡，用床位地址最安全"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T09:58:23.000Z","msg":"你搵緊咩工"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T09:59:03.000Z","